	<p class="cyberpunk inverse dotted scannedh">
		Improper error handling flaws occur when an error message that's displayed to an end user provides clues about how an application or website operates. Although messages like this can help developers fix problems on their sites, they also show attackers information that they can use to help them break into the application.
